snippet: Chile sought help from foreign security agencies in identifying those responsible for an explosion that injured 14 people at a subway station in the capital, while bomb scares and small blasts kept the country on edge Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Chile Seeks Foreign Help in Subway Bombing Case
headline.main: Chile Seeks Foreign Help in Subway Bombing Case

lead_paragraph: Chile sought help from foreign security agencies in identifying those responsible for an explosion that injured 14 people at a subway station in the capital, while bomb scares and small blasts kept the country on edge Wednesday.
